# Clinic Project Documentation (file.mdf)

## Project Overview

- **Name:** عيادة د. هالة (Dr. Halla Clinic)
- **Type:** Appointment Booking System
- **Version:** 1.0.0
- **Stack:** Laravel 12 (API) + React 18 (SPA frontend pending) + MySQL
- **Auth:** Laravel Sanctum (SPA stateful API)
- **Broadcasting:** Pusher (WebSockets)
- **Queue:** sync (dev), database (prod)
- **Cache:** database
- **Session:** database

---

