## API Endpoints (24 total)

### Public (7)
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | /api/register | Register new patient (name, email, password, password_confirmation, phone, date_of_birth, gender, address) |
| POST | /api/login | Login (email, password) -> token |
| GET | /api/slots?date= | Available time slots for date |
| GET | /api/cms/about | Active about section |
| GET | /api/cms/courses | Active courses (sorted) |
| GET | /api/cms/videos | Active videos (sorted) |
| GET | /api/cms/certifications | Active certifications (sorted) |
| GET | /api/cms/posts | Active posts (sorted) |
| GET | /api/cms/posts/{id} | Single post |

### Authenticated (Patient/Admin) (13)
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | /api/logout | Revoke current token |
| GET | /api/user | Current user with patient profile |
| GET | /api/bookings | List bookings (own or all if admin), filter by status, paginated 20 |
| POST | /api/bookings | Create appointment (appointment_date, start_time, end_time, patient_notes) |
| GET | /api/bookings/{id} | View single appointment (ownership check) |
| PATCH | /api/bookings/{id}/status | Approve/reject (admin only) |
| GET | /api/notifications | Paginated 20 |
| PATCH | /api/notifications/{id}/read | Mark single read |
| POST | /api/notifications/mark-all-read | Mark all read |
| GET | /api/working-hours | Get all working hours ordered |
| PUT | /api/working-hours | Update schedule (admin, truncate+bulk insert) |
| PUT | /api/cms/about | Update about (admin) |
| POST | /api/cms/posts | Create post (admin) |
| PUT | /api/cms/posts/{id} | Update post (admin) |
| DELETE | /api/cms/posts/{id} | Delete post (admin) |
| POST | /api/upload | Upload image (max 20MB, jpeg/png/jpg/gif/webp) (admin) |
| POST | /api/upload-video | Upload video (max 200MB, mp4/mov/avi/webm/mkv) (admin) |

### Admin CMS (9)
| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| POST | /api/cms/courses | Create course |
| PUT | /api/cms/courses/{id} | Update course |
| DELETE | /api/cms/courses/{id} | Delete course |
| POST | /api/cms/videos | Create video |
| PUT | /api/cms/videos/{id} | Update video |
| DELETE | /api/cms/videos/{id} | Delete video |
| POST | /api/cms/certifications | Create certification |
| PUT | /api/cms/certifications/{id} | Update certification |
| DELETE | /api/cms/certifications/{id} | Delete certification |

