## Recent Changes (Session 2026-05-13)

### 1. Notification Bell – Admin Redirect with Appointment Highlight
- **File:** `frontend/src/components/NotificationBell.jsx`
- Admin clicking an appointment notification navigates to `/admin?appointment_id=X`
- Admin clicking a **subscription** notification (`data.subscription_id`) opens the existing modal showing patient name + post title
- Dropdown closes automatically before navigation/modal

### 2. AdminDashboard – Highlighted Row from Notification
- **File:** `frontend/src/pages/AdminDashboard.jsx`
- Reads `?appointment_id=` from URL query params
- Highlights matching row with a pulsing green glow animation (`pulseBorder` keyframes)
- Auto-scrolls to the highlighted row (`scrollIntoView` smooth)

### 3. Completed Appointment Status
- **Enum:** `app/Enums/AppointmentStatus.php` — added `Completed = 'completed'`
- **Endpoint:** `POST /api/bookings/complete-past` — moves all `approved` appointments with `appointment_date < today` to `completed`
- **Controller:** `BookingController@completePast` — admin-only batch update
- **Frontend:** AdminDashboard auto-calls `completePast` on mount (silent), then fetches bookings
- **Translation:** Added `status_completed` ("مكتمل") and `completed_past` to `lang/ar/messages.php`
- **Filter button:** "مكتمل" filter added to AdminDashboard
- **Styling:** Completed status uses gray (neutral, not blue)

### 4. Posts Page – Disable "احجز الجلسة" When Already Subscribed
- **File:** `frontend/src/pages/PostsPage.jsx`
- Removed `{!post.is_subscribed && ...}` wrapper (button always rendered)
- Button is disabled when `post.is_subscribed` is true
- Text shows `"تم الحجز"` (Already booked) instead of `"احجز الجلسة"`
- Spots-full (`available_spots === 0`) shows `"ممتلئ"` (Full) — unchanged

### 5. Table Alignment Fixes
- **File:** `frontend/src/pages/AdminDashboard.jsx`
- Patient column: `text-left` / header `text-left`
- Email, Date, Time, Status, Actions columns: `text-center` / headers `text-center`

